1. Description

The app contains physical properties of 15 major industrial gases as well as a conversion calculator for the major units.

2. Technology

The app is written in HTML based on the dojo toolkit mobile framework. It is tested  on Gecko based browsers. 


3. Demo site

The demo site is at http://h2217974.stratoserver.net/tools/combined/Germany/en, alt. http://h2217974.stratoserver.net/tools/combined/Germany/de . Depending on the language settings of your browser a different language version is shown


